<title>smʿt ṣwtk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (smʿt ṣwtk byṣạrḥny fy klmtk bwḍwḥ ndtny wqlt ʿạyzk tbqy̱ kạml
 kẖlytny ạ̉fwq wlmạ smʿt wṣytk wạ̉nạ tḥt ạ̉mrk yạ yswʿ hbdạ̉ wạ̉ḥạwl)2
 ạlqrạr - (wʿsẖạn bḥbk wʿd mny kl mạ fy̱ ạ̉yạmy lyk
 zy ṭfl ạ̹msk ạ̹ydyạ yạlly kl rjạyạ fyk)2
 2- (ạlkmạl msẖ ḥạjh ṣʿbh mstḥylh ạlkmạl ạ̹ny ạ̉ʿysẖ ṭạlb rḍạk
 tfḍl mʿạyạ fy rḥlẗ ạlʿmr ạlṭwylh wtrwy qlby ḥb mn ạ̉nhạr gẖnạk)2
 3- (ʿyny sẖạft ḥbk ạ̹tʿlqt byh mn sạʿthạ frḥt wzrʿt ạlậmạl
 wfy ṣlạtk ywmạty ḥby wqrby lyk hmạ ạ̉wl kẖṭwh fy ṭryq ạlkmạl)2</lyrics>
